videos.headline: UConn's Thomas makes spectacular diving catch
videos.description: Connecticut wide receiver Noel Thomas beats two Central Florida defenders and makes a great diving grab in Knights' territory.

videos.headline: UCF cuts deficit with 22-yard TD
videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton throws through two UConn defenders to find Dredrick Snelson for a 22-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: UCF TE catches 19-yard TD over defender
videos.description: McKenzie Milton lofts a pass to TE Jordan Akins, who goes up high over a UConn defender for the TD.

videos.headline: Milton's third TD give UCF the lead
